@NODE "Mail_2" "Yet Another Progress Indicator"
From: "Tony Rolfe" <edgewater@shoalhaven.net.au>
Organization: Edgewater Motel, Burrill Lake, NSW 2539 Australia
Date: 28 Jan 99 09:37:24 +1000
Subject: Yet Another Progress Indicator

