Hmm, another really bodgy way :

(I am -so- great for stupid ideas:)

Print the text to a hidden bitmap, then grab each column of the text as a=

shape, and blit it where you need it, but each column after is blitted on=
e
pixel higher or lower than the last =3D]

You can also do this sideways for some really bad italics ;]

