You wouldn`t. rtgmaster.library is an alternative to using the OS (or
the blitz methods) you can`t mix the two without using c2p or p2c. That
would be a silly thing to do since it would ruin the reason for using
rtgmaster in the first place. I`ve not actually used rtgmaster myself,
I never saw a reason to do so and the mildred lib gives you even less
incentive.

