 Heya,

 If you set ANY task PRI to the highest possible, nothing crashes but all
functions stop working except for thsoe required for the program.

 EVERYTHING, software clocks, the mouse, all functioning libraries, disk
drives.. If your lucky you might be able to open a shell within around 1 mabye
2 minutes (if you have a Hotkey for it) to fix the problem.

 Its legendary when your decoding MP3's, because it goes much faster :)

