 I probably should also have mentioned that to wait for more message ports=
simply keep ORing them into the parameter for the Wait_ command, and add l=
oops 
in to process them if you detect one, i.e. If (signal &xxx)...


|) /\ \/ ][ |)   |\/| =A9 |\/| ][ |\| |\|
