I have this code:

***

Bitmapinput   ;it's in Blitz mode
Print "Enter Your Name:"
Locate 6,5
name$=Edit$("   ",3)

***

Then I have nested 'if''s to see where in a highscore table name$
goes...

My problem is that the second time I run this, the program freezes. It
writes 'Enter Your Name';
Then the cursor appears underneath it, but it doesn't pick up keyboard
presses.

Am I missing something obvious? Is there a way of 'reseting' name$?



Thanks in advance

James


