  Wait on, I remember something now :) I think that #Edit$# (from
memory) is buggy with Blitz mode (even though you've come out of Blitz
mode and gone into Amiga mode). You have to make your own text parser
using #Inkey$# (and check for the enter key #Chr$#(11) etc).
   But still do the #Blitzkeys# #On/Off# thing as well, or you'll still
have problems with #Inkey$.#

  Seeya- Anton

