dskdatr   EQU $008 ; ER        P   Disk data early read (dummy address)
joy0dat   EQU $00A ; R      D      Joystick-mouse 0 data (vert,horiz)
jot1dat   EQU $00C ; R      D      Joystick-mouse 1 data (vert,horiz)
