aMIGA_dUDE wrote:
> 
> I am think of giving my progey's local support.  How would I
> implement this in to progey's in Blitz?

When adding locale support to Foundation i used three methods. First
I used the locale.library which was nice and os friendly, then i made
my own buffered locale system for added control. Then i decided to
scrap all the methods and use an array of strings! It used more memory
(a few extra k or so) but it`s nice, simple and fast to deal with.

Cheers,

