Hello Christophe

Where is the piece of code to get the records ? Don't forget that EOF wor=
ks when you reach for the first time the end of the file. If you continue=
 to get records past the end of the file, you may not get EOF again. Be a=
lso careful with the open statement (successful or not), and close the fi=
les when necessary.

Regards
