Hello again,
	in all honesty, I got the idea from GeneticSpecies, because the
intro is a cdxl file. The startup-script has

playanim* lmbabort view multipal dosxl xlspeed=250 gs.intro

*this is just cdgsxl renamed

so if you do a

Execute_ "cdgsxl lmbabort view multipal dosxl xlspeed=150 advert.xl",0,0

I've discovered that xl's can be placed in the game at any point. Cool for
cut scenes!
n.b. the difference in the xlspeed is because I was using the CD32 advert xl
to test the code.

Chris


